= Roll

Roll is a library manager for Ruby. Code repositories
can be made visible to Ruby just by setting an
environment variable.


== How to Install

Rolls needs to be downloaded and installed manually via the setup script provided.

  $ tar -xvzf roll-x.y.z
  $ cd roll-x.y.z
  $ sudo task/setup

On Windows, this last line needs to be 'ruby task/setup'.


